quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  100,1,"By the galloping, panting horses"
  100,2,"striking sparks of fire [with their hooves]"
  100,3,launching raids at dawn
  100,4,stirring up thereby clouds of dust
  100,5,plunging thereby into the midst of the enemy
  100,6,"indeed, man is very ungrateful to his Lord –"
  100,7,and he himself is a witness to that –
  100,8,and he is truly extreme in his love of wealth
  100,9,Does he not know that the contents of graves will be overturned
  100,10,and the secrets of the hearts will be brought to light
  100,11,"Indeed, their Lord is All-Aware of them on that Day"